import React from 'react' import "../../styles/archive.css" import ImageTile from '../ImageTile' import NavBar from '../NavBar' import { useEffect, useState } from "react" import { db } from '../firebase/config' import { collection, getDocs } from 'firebase/firestore' const Archive = () => { const [mugs, setMugs] = useState(null) useEffect(() => { const ref = collection(db, 'mugs') getDocs(ref) }, []) return (
{mugs}
) } export default Archive
